column3: Reach flowpath subtype representing an observed stream flowpath. It is equivalent to Observed for networkFlowType for a Water Linear Flow in the NHN.

Reach flowpath subtype representing a flowpath that appears to traverse the land but was not visible when mapped. It is equivalent to Constructed for networkFlowType for a Water Linear Flow in the NHN. Flow through dams that are assigned a Constructed value will require manual review.
Unknown, impossible to determine, or unrelated to the other existing subtypes. It is equivalent to Unknown or None for networkFlowType for a Water Linear Flow in the NHN.
